Kannada AoA Study Milestone Report

Katrina May Dulay

15/04/2021

Kannada AoA Study Milestone Report

This milestone report summarizes the results of the Kannada AoA study.

Milestone hit: N > 30. This report is based on data from 31 participants.

14 completed the old Qualtrics form and 17 completed the new Qualtrics form.

Data errors were manually corrected with 3 participants due to:

  1. Wrong demographic entry: Parent marked self as expert

  2. Missing ID due to Qualtrics login issues: RA manually filled up demographic + practice session [verified correct by Promise RA & Oxford RO]

  3. Wrong demographic entry: Expert marked only disordered population

Supporting documentation:

  1. Data dictionary

  2. Word list properties (verified)

  3. Data correction log (from RA documentation)

Next steps:

  1. Milestone report for N = 50 and N = 74.

  2. Interrater reliability computations.

  3. Decision parameters for dropping words and participants, if any.

  4. Analysis plan for AoA manuscript using mixed effect models.
